steps to follow connection of git and GitHub
Create repo

Clone repo
git clone https URL
git remote remove origin

Make git configuration
git config --global user.name
git config --global user.email
git config --global --list

generate ssh key
ssh-keygen -t ed25519/rsa -C "message"
Add key to GitHub 
git remote add origin ssh URl
git remote -v
ssh -T git@github.com

Push and pull file by check branch..
